                <i class="fas fa-info-circle mr-2"></i> important information
            </button>
            <div x-show="open" class="mt-2 text-gray-400">
                <p>
                    you should watch
                    <a href="https://www.crunchyroll.com/de/series/GXJHM3P19/bocchi-the-rock" target="_blank" class="text-[#5865f2] hover:text-[#4752c4] transition">bocchi the rock</a> :) 
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
